@AnnaNeMussss @BasilHammer @PeterSweden7 There's an old phrase, "two weeks to slow the spread" have you heard this before anywhere?  

What matters is energy available and energy consumed. Combine a reduction of availability with an increase in consumption and what do you get?  

"Green energy"

@QuaiNetwork 
POW requires high energy consumption and longer processing time while POS requires low energy consumption alternatives to the POW algorithm. My favorite consensus mechanism  is POS because it consume energy at low cost

